Bakery1908 — Digital Experience Concept
This project is an interactive concept redesign for Bakery1908’s website.

The goal:
Transform the current static menu into an immersive, conversion-driven experience.

Key ideas:
- Interactive product browsing (hover, tilt, expand)
- Mobile-first discovery UX
- AI-powered order assistant
- Performance-optimized (Next.js direction)

This is not a final product — it is a live concept prototype to demonstrate the potential direction.
